      "index": 2,
      "text": "Over the previous months we have received reports of coordinated pirate attacks both inside and outside our borders that originated from the Deep Periphery, by a group that has been called 'Harbingers'.\n\nThese attacks resulted in the loss of JumpShips and communication with our outer worlds while the raiders are advancing to our capital, Coromodir.",
